12.  June 28, 2024
    
    ## Hybrid AI Search is Ready

title: MemFree
text:
![memfree hybrid ai search](https://www.memfree.me/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fchangelog%2Fhybrid-ai-search.png&w=1920&q=75)
    
    Today, MemFree supports Hybrid AI Search
    
    ### [](#what-is-hybrid-ai-search)What is Hybrid AI Search?

title: MemFree
text:
Hybrid AI Search involves simultaneously performing searches on your personal knowledge base (such as bookmarks, notes, documents, etc.) and the Internet. This approach enables the retrieval of context that best matches your question, allowing a large AI model to provide the most accurate answer possible.
    
    ### [](#why-do-you-need-hybrid-ai-search)Why do you need Hybrid AI Search?

title: MemFree
text:
1.  **Personalization**: The search results are tailored to your personal knowledge base, which is more relevant to you.
    2.  **Efficiency**: You can quickly find the information you need without having to search multiple sources.
    3.  **Accuracy**: The AI model can provide more accurate answers by considering both your personal knowledge base and the Internet.

title: MemFree
text: 4.  **Real-time Updates**: Provides access to the latest information through Internet searches, ensuring timeliness and relevance.

title: MemFree
text: As shown in the figure, I first indexed the webpage [https://www.memfree.me/blog/memfree-build-1-why](https://www.memfree.me/blog/memfree-build-1-why), so when I ask Why Build MemFree, Hybrid AI Search will first consider the content of the memfree blog, and then consider various content searched from the Internet.

title: MemFree
text:
Now, you can ask any questions and get the most accurate answers from MemFree Hybrid AI Search. Enjoy!
    
13.  June 22, 2024
    
    ## AI Search based on Internet content
    
    ![memfree hybrid ai search web](https://www.memfree.me/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fchangelog%2Fai-search-web.png&w=1920&q=75)
    
    Today, MemFree supports AI Search and Ask based on Internet content.

title: MemFree
text:
when you ask a question, MemFree will:
    
    1.  Search the internet for the most relevant information by multi search engines
    2.  Search the internet for the most relevant images by multi search engines
    3.  Let LLM summarize the information and give you the best answer

title: MemFree
text: 4.  Let LLM generate some related questions about the your question, You can keep asking questions until you get all the answers you like.
